7 An Act relating to the Oklahoma National Guard
Educational Assistance Act; amending Section 1,
8 Chapter 24, O.S.L. 2022 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section
3231), which relates to creation of the act;
9 directing certain assistance to include program fees
and any other fees for courses; directing the
10 Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education and the
Military Department of the State of Oklahoma to
11 jointly review certain fees; allowing the State
Regents to determine if certain fees are ineligible
12 for program assistance; authorizing the Department to
establish certain cap; modifying retention
13 eligibility; authorizing the Department to establish
a cap on certain program participation; modifying
14 reasons for which an application for assistance may
be denied; directing the Department to promulgate
15 certain regulations; directing the State Regents and
the Department to coordinate certain promulgation;
16 updating statutory references; updating statutory
language; providing an effective date; and declaring
17 an emergency.
18
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 24, O.S.L. 2022
21 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 3231), is amended to read as follows:
22 Section 3231. A. This act shall be known and may be cited as
23 the “Oklahoma National Guard Educational Assistance Act”.
24
